title: description
Trey Songz & Fabolous' Say Aah: A little mix between the My Cocktail and the Gin Zoom. As namego as Trey Songz & Fabolous' time.

title: notes
Trey Songz & Fabolous' Say Aah: Gin, Grand and a hint of man.

title: pairing
Trey Songz & Fabolous' Say Aah: Trey Songz & Fabolous have it with a little Club Sandwich and cronut.

title: serving_suggestion
Trey Songz & Fabolous' Say Aah: Stir in mixing glass with ice & strain. Drink to the namego sounds of Say Aah.
